<a href="/questions/955413-what-page-to-i-find-in-what-way-is-a">What page to I find in what way is a Christian life a paradox?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_955413'><a id="like_count_community_question_955413" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/955413?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F672493.The_Pursuit_of_God">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
