<span id="freeTextContainer9210670252944850008">I would recommend this to any Christian. In fact, once I finished, I ran down to Barnes &amp; Noble and bought 2 extra copies for friends. <br/><br/>I took my time to read it (4.5 months). Read it, shared excerpts with others, meditated on it. <br/><br/>This explores the importance of passion in seeking God by a man who lived with passion for God. It is so easy to get distracted by a noisy and demanding world and this book is spiritual succour<br/><br/></span>

